  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EStructuralFeature.Internal.DynamicValueHolder, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject, CarLikeOdometry

    public class CarLikeOdometryImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements CarLikeOdometry
    An implementation of the model object 'Car Like Odometry'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Header
    • Steering angle
    • Left rear wheel distance
    • Right rear wheel distance
    • Right rear wheel velocity
    • Left rear wheel velocity
